# Repo Hardening Plan

## Purpose

This document tracks the next documentation hardening phase for the SBXQIAO Infrastructure Lab.

The goal is to move the repository from a good structural baseline to a complete operational source of truth by:
- completing host records
- expanding validation evidence
- improving deployment journaling
- strengthening standards consistency
- making future troubleshooting and handover easier

---

## Success Criteria

This hardening phase is complete when:

- every active host has a complete host record
- every core service has a validation record
- deployment records show what was done, not only the current state
- standards documents are detailed enough to guide future changes
- checkpoints exist for major stable milestones
- documentation matches the real implemented environment

